description: Do not use // ignore or // ignore_for_file in this project
alwaysApply: true
---

# No analyzer ignore comments

Do **not** add `// ignore: rule_name` or `// ignore_for_file: ...` anywhere in this codebase.

- Fix the underlying issue (code or style) so the lint passes, or
- Disable the rule for the project in `analysis_options_custom.yaml` under "Add your custom rule overrides below".

Never introduce new ignore comments.
